---
import { Send, Terminal } from 'lucide-react';
---

<section id="contacto" class="py-24 px-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
  
  <div class="bg-stibios-surface border border-stibios-border rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden">
    
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.02)_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.02)_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:32px_32px] pointer-events-none"></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12">
      
      <div class="flex-1">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-stibios-accent text-xs font-mono mb-6 border border-stibios-accent/20 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-stibios-accent/5">
          <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-stibios-accent animate-pulse"></div>
          OPEN FOR WORK
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-stibios-text mb-4">
          Inicia el <br />
          <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-stibios-text to-stibios-dim">Protocolo de Proyecto</span>
        </h2>
        
        <p class="text-stibios-dim leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Cuéntame qué estás construyendo. Ya sea un SaaS complejo, una web corporativa o una idea loca. Analizaré la viabilidad técnica y te responderé en 24h.
        </p>

        <div class="font-mono text-xs text-stibios-dim/50">
            <p>LOCATION: REMOTE / WORLDWIDE</p>
            <p>LATENCY: &lt; 24H RESPONSE</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex-1">
        <form class="space-y-4">
          
          <div class="space-y-1">
            <label for="name" class="text-xs font-mono text-stibios-dim ml-1">VAR: CLIENT_NAME</label>
            <input 
              type="text" 
              id="name" 
              name="name" 
              placeholder="Tu nombre o Empresa"
              class="w-full bg-stibios-bg border border-stibios-border rounded p-3 text-stibios-text focus:border-stibios-accent focus:ring-1 focus:ring-stibios-accent outline-none transition-all placeholder:text-stibios-border"
              required
            />
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-1">
            <label for="email" class="text-xs font-mono text-stibios-dim ml-1">VAR: EMAIL_ADDRESS</label>
            <input 
              type="email" 
              id="email" 
              name="email" 
              placeholder="hola@empresa.com"
              class="w-full bg-stibios-bg border border-stibios-border rounded p-3 text-stibios-text focus:border-stibios-accent focus:ring-1 focus:ring-stibios-accent outline-none transition-all placeholder:text-stibios-border"
              required
            />
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-1">
            <label for="message" class="text-xs font-mono text-stibios-dim ml-1">FUNC: PROJECT_DETAILS()</label>
            <textarea 
              id="message" 
              name="message" 
              rows="4" 
              placeholder="Describe tu proyecto..."
              class="w-full bg-stibios-bg border border-stibios-border rounded p-3 text-stibios-text focus:border-stibios-accent focus:ring-1 focus:ring-stibios-accent outline-none transition-all placeholder:text-stibios-border resize-none"
              required
            ></textarea>
          </div>

          <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-stibios-text text-stibios-bg font-bold py-3 rounded hover:bg-white transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-2 group">
            <Terminal size={18} />
            <span>EJECUTAR ENVÍO</span>
            <Send size={16} className="group-hover:translate-x-1 group-hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform opacity-60" />
          </button>

        </form>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>